---
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="lineage">
  <div class="lineage-container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="lineage-header">
      <h2 class="lineage-heading animate-on-scroll text-reveal">
        Kwan Um škola Zen buddhizmu
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards Column Layout -->
    <div class="lineage-cards">
      <!-- Card 1: East Asian Buddhism -->
      <div class="lineage-card animate-on-scroll fade-in-up stagger-1">
        <div class="card-number">01</div>
        <h3 class="card-heading">Východoázijský Zen</h3>
        <div class="card-text">
          <p>
            Zen buddhizmus má svoje korene v <span class="text-highlight">Číne</span>, kde vznikol ako Chan
            v 6. storočí. Odtiaľ sa rozšíril do <span class="text-highlight">Japonska</span> (Zen)
            a <span class="text-highlight">Kórey</span> (Seon), kde sa stal dominantnou formou buddhizmu.
          </p>
          <p>
            Táto tradícia kladie dôraz na <span class="text-bold">priamu skúsenosť reality</span> namiesto
            štúdia textov. Základom je meditácia v sede, práca s koánmi a integrácia
            praxe do každodenného života. Zen sa nezaoberá abstraktnými teóriami,
            ale priamym pozorovaním vlastnej mysle.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Kwan Um School - offset to right -->
      <div class="lineage-card lineage-card-offset animate-on-scroll fade-in-up stagger-2">
        <div class="card-number">02</div>
        <h3 class="card-heading">Kwan Um škola</h3>
        <div class="card-text">
          <p>
            Kwan Um School of Zen je medzinárodná škola kórejského zen buddhizmu,
            ktorú založil veľmajster Seung Sahn v roku 1983. Škola spája
            tradičné <span class="text-bold">kórejské metódy</span> s moderným prístupom
            prístupným pre západných praktikujúcich.
          </p>
          <p>
            Dnes má Kwan Um centrá vo viac ako <span class="text-highlight"><span class="counter" data-count="30">30</span> krajinách</span> sveta.
            Na Slovensku pôsobíme v Košiciach a Bratislave, s menšími skupinami
            v Piešťanoch, Liptovskom Mikuláši a Malackách. Organizujeme pravidelné
            meditácie, ústrania a stretnutia v celej Európe.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .lineage-container {
    max-width: 60rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Header */
  .lineage-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .lineage-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-family-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-normal);
  }

  /* Cards Column Layout */
  .lineage-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3.5rem;
  }

  .lineage-card {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }

  .lineage-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3) 0%, transparent 100%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .lineage-card > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .lineage-card:hover {
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-6px) perspective(1000px) rotateX(1deg);
  }

  .lineage-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Second card offset to right - hierarchy visual */
  .lineage-card-offset {
    margin-left: 5rem;
    /* Keep same width as first card */
    max-width: calc(100% - 5rem);
  }

  .card-number {
    font-family: var(--font-family-display);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-light);
    color: var(--color-stone-300);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .card-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-family-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
    line-height: var(--line-height-tight);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .card-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-6);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .card-text p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-light);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-loose);
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-normal);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .text-bold {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: #1c1917;
  }

  .text-highlight {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: #44403c;
  }

  .counter {
    display: inline-block;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    min-width: 2ch;
  }

  /* Mobile Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .lineage-container {
      padding: 0 var(--spacing-4);
    }

    .lineage-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .lineage-cards {
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .lineage-card {
      padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    }

    /* Remove offset on mobile */
    .lineage-card-offset {
      margin-left: 0;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .card-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);
    }

    .card-heading {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
    }

    .card-text {
      gap: var(--spacing-5);
    }
  }

  /* Tablet */
  @media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
    .lineage-card {
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    }

    .lineage-card-offset {
      margin-left: 3rem;
      max-width: calc(100% - 3rem);
    }

    .lineage-cards {
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
